    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Built works, particularly in a modern urban environment, that have emerged from anonymous creators, inspired by the desire to build things or to modify and personalize space. Spontaneous architecture is communal and social, often exploring non-traditional construction materials and with immediate technology.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
